OL,6,FPlaces with the highest pay such as
OL,7,FLondon and Cambridge were said to have
OL,8,Fmore than twice as many cutting-edge
OL,9,Ffirms and three times as many cutting-
OL,10,Fedge jobs in sectors like biotech and
OL,11,FAI than low-pay places such as
OL,12,FBurnley, Huddersfield and
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough.
