OL,4,Crevealed
OL,6,FOut of the 63 largest towns and
OL,7,Fcities, nearly all those with above-
OL,8,Faverage salaries for the UK are in the
OL,9,FSouth East, including Reading and
OL,10,FMilton Keynes, with seven places in
OL,11,Fthe rest of the country having
OL,12,Fsalaries above the UK average ` Leeds,
OL,13,FWarrington, Derby, Swindon, Bristol,
OL,14,FAberdeen and Edinburgh, said the
OL,15,Freport.
OL,17,FAndrew Carter, chief executive of
OL,18,FCentre for Cities, said: "The
OL,19,FGovernment is right to identify
OL,20,Fboosting economic growth for every
OL,21,Fpart of the country as a top priority.
