OL,6,F"The stark nature of our findings
OL,7,Fshows an incremental approach is not
OL,8,Fgoing to be enough.
OL,10,F"Boldness, urgency and scale are
OL,11,Fcrucial. 2025 needs to be a year for
OL,12,Fdelivery, particularly on the
OL,13,FGovernment's Industrial Strategy,
OL,14,Fframework for English devolution and
OL,15,Fits reforms to planning.
OL,17,F"Bold changes to planning rules can
OL,18,Fdeliver more housing in the most
OL,19,Fexpensive places and in our big
OL,20,Fcities, where it's needed most.
